name: Bobby Dexter
description: I am a God fearing man who is Lead by God ..To know that you can feel what love really is; to know, to feel, to love.I am a charismatic sincere and honest man who believes and values morals and respect in a relationship.i enjoy meeting new friends and would like to find that special one to share life’s ups and downs with. I am secure in myself and have learned to walk rather than run into relationships. I offer honesty and loyalty as well as respect and compassion.I am a good listener and enjoy conversation. I am a man with a big heart. I would like to find someone with sincere and caring heart. someone with values and a big heart. One that will not consider distance to be a hindrance in a relationship.
